      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eWater Demand Optimization \u0026 Forecasting App for Business Users\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      This app empowers business users to monitor and forecast water demand by analyzing operational and environmental data.\r\n      Using machine learning models, it identifies over-usage patterns based on key variables such as employee count, pipe\r\n      infrastructure, abstraction levels, and processing water consumption. The insights enable efficient resource allocation,\r\n      regulatory compliance, and sustainable water management.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eYour data\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \r\n      \r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Trained Model \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Excess Usage Prediction: Binary or categorical prediction of whether usage exceeds demand\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Feature Importance: Visual rankings of which variables most influence over-demand\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Training Metrics: Model evaluation results to gauge prediction reliability\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Distribution \u0026 Correlation Insights\r\n      \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Operational Optimization: Detecting over-usage patterns enables better planning and water conservation measures\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Sustainability \u0026 Compliance: Supports environmental compliance by identifying over-abstraction risks\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Data-Driven Action: Insights guide resource allocation, pipe maintenance, and staffing decisions\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Flexibility: Users can tailor models and features to align with facility type and industry size\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Usability: Intuitive workflows for both analysts and business users ensure fast deployment and minimal training required\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
